				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Hi folks, this was sort of tipped off by the other thread, but i've been hearing you other veteran beastlords talk more and more about suspend minion.  My question is, i'm sitting at around 50aaxp points.  I'm considering going and getting CA and CS, but I'm considering suspend minion more and more.  I also play on a pvp server so that would make the benefits of suspend minion even larger.
<br />

<br />
