				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">YEs you will. If you zone, die, LD or logout you will lose the suspended pet. One nice feature is if you die and run back to the zone where your corpse is, you can summon and buff a pet then suspend it. Then accept the rez and then unsuspend the pet you will now have a pet summoned with the free mana after death.<br />_________________<br /><img src=http://www.mbray.inet.net.nz/sig/bukar_sig.gif>
