				<td colspan="2"><hr /></td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">There are two main ways to use this aa.  You can back up a pet just in case one dies.  This can be a lifesaver if you solo a lot.  The other is to save a pet through getting rez'd (in the same zone) or through invis'ing.  When suspended, the pet is basically gone from play (as if you didn't have a pet) until you bring it back.  I use a lot when I'm soloing or pulling with a smallish size group in an area with a lot of wanders so I can pull while invis without losing my pet.
<br />

<br />
The aa will not work if your pet is on any mobs hate list or if it is too far away.
<br />

<br />
Rankorr</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
